    <h4>Application Procedure :</h4>
    <ul>
     <li>Visit the homepage of Pradhan Mantri Jan Dhan Yojana portal</li>
     <li>Fill up the application form.</li>
     <li>download the application form for Pradhan Mantri Jan Dhan Yojana from the scheme’s official website.</li>
     <li>submit it at the local bank branch.</li>
     <li>You will also have to provide some documents along with the form to avail this scheme.</li>

   </ul>  
    
    </div>
